{"tid":472170,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個你覺得無線欠佢一個獎既tvb既藝人","createTime":"2017-11-18T03:33:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T02:58:55.000Z","uid":58319,"like":7,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"fb922c1fe892228466e2707786671d1c0f3a6ea9","tid":472170,"uid":58319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T03:33:08.000Z","msg":"馬德鐘<br />\n馬國明<br />\n馬浚偉<br />\n<br />\n第一個撈左20年豬肉獎都冇個<br />\n第二個都係撈左20年，係近兩年先分到豬肉獎<br />\n第三個拎親都係豬肉獎，次次都同視帝無緣"},{"pid":"81efeb5cf1aec71482441557e7da1be7b22a7d1f","tid":472170,"uid":131259,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:01:19.000Z","msg":"佢地根本唔care"},{"pid":"3dcac5bdee49539be09f136971e07e136fecf8d2","tid":472170,"uid":102562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:09:36.000Z","msg":"認字特警"},{"pid":"7940fc48b0ae5256a94fa7e54f211a7fbd9666d4","tid":472170,"uid":81569,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:11:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢地根本唔care</blockquote><br />\n點會唔care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n馬浚偉電台公開講過自己想拎視帝"},{"pid":"169b1a30b37c016602465bcdd20f95a0bde62c3d","tid":472170,"uid":58319,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:13:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢地根本唔care</blockquote><br />\n點會唔care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n馬浚偉電台公開講過自己想拎視帝</blockquote><br />\n未係囉，邊會有員工撈左20年，但豬肉獎都分唔到一個，望住班新生代入行2-3年已經拎哂獎，再望下同期果啲，咩7獎都拎過哂，點會care，葡萄死啦<br />\n係馬明先咁好仔繼續留守比人恰"},{"pid":"0be7315ad54b17306cd706a7c384740f39daf2a0","tid":472170,"uid":94828,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:15:33.000Z","msg":"林峰既視帝"},{"pid":"f1e267e55c6fd1a5a4ca6fceb1e9703eccb79858","tid":472170,"uid":56623,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:18:40.000Z","msg":"馬德鐘 鳳凰四重奏個年最應該拎 最後比左鄭嘉穎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}